Teal





Brown





Oatmeal


 














Details


	The Madeley loveseat provides a cozy place to curl up solo or welcome a friend for a chat. High flared arms, two loose back pillows and reversible jacquard accent pillows offer just the right support while deep seating and soft chenille fabric, with a cozy feel, adds to the high level of comfort. Loose back cushions and seat cushions are reversible to extend the life of the loveseat. The teal color and welted seams offer a casual contemporary look.


	100% Polyester.






